{"name": "stakeout", "metadata": {"name": "stakeout", "version": "1.0.1", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "A tool to inspect source code ownership.", "upload_time": 1733204268}, "documentation": ["Stakeout\n========\n\nThis project allows you to inspect the ownership of a project using the OWNERSHIP file.\n\nUsage\n-----\n\nFull inspection\n\n```bash\n> stakeout .\nUnowned: 300\n@team-a: 1200\n@team-b: 4000\nTotal: number of files: 5000\n```\n\nInspect a single file or directory\n\n```bash\n> stakeout . --file=README.md\n@team-a\n```\n\nList all files owned by a single team\n\n```bash\n> stakeout . --team=team-a\n./README.md\n```\n\nDevelop\n-------\n\n```bash\npython3 -m venv .env\nsource ./env/bin/activate\npython3 -m pip install -r requirements.txt\n```\n\nDistribute\n----------\n\n```bash\npython3 -m build\npython3 -m twine upload dist/*\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "stakeout.main", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "stakeout.main.run", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Runs the program"]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "stakeout", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "stakeout.stakeout", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "stakeout.stakeout.main", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "root_raw", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "path", "type": {"name": "str | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "owner", "type": {"name": "str | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Reads the path to inspect along with an optional file to find ownership for or the team for which to file files"]}, {"name": "stakeout.stakeout.list_all_files", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "path", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "original_root", "type": nul